name: Def Star
description:
Limited Edition of 1.

Featuring a chest print of the classic Def Jam Recordings logo. Old school shit.

Comes with embroidered One Eye Deer Logos on front bottom left and centre of the back of the neck area of the garment & One Eye Deer badge.

Size: Medium (62cm top to bottom, 47cm across body when laid on a flat surface).
